## ğŸ“Œ When Should You Use a Module?

| Situation                                 | Use a module?   |
| ----------------------------------------- | --------------- |
| Your file is too long (300+ lines)        | âœ… Yes           |
| You want to reuse code in another project | âœ… Yes           |
| You work in a team with many files        | âœ… Yes           |
| Your script is small (20â€“50 lines)        | âŒ Not necessary |

